If you wish to create and start a new JMXConnectorServer in your server app, then you will need 
first to create/start an RMI registry. If you do create and start a JMXConnectorServer on the server side,
then you must either not pass the -Dcom.sun.management.jmxremote.* properties, or use another port 
number for your own connector server, orthewise the two servers (your own, and the default agent) 
will compete for the same port number.











